net.sf.jguiraffe.examples.tutorial.mainwnd

Class MainWndController

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jguiraffe.examples.tutorial.mainwnd.MainWndController

  • public class MainWndController
extends Object

    The controller class for the main window.

    This class implements logic related to the GUI of the main window of the JGUIraffe tutorial application.

    Version:
    $Id: MainWndController.java 205 2012-01-29 18:29:57Z oheger $
    Author:
    Oliver Heger
